[[module ListPages name="isabels-happy-meal" tags="-joke"]]
|| **Tale (Rating):** [[[isabels-happy-meal| Shortened for brevity]]] (+%%rating%%) || **Date:** 30 June 2019 ||
||||= **Details** ||
||||< Dr. Isabel Wondertainment, V offers to assist Chef Chad Ambrose with a problem he's having with his unicorn steak supplier, purely out of the goodness of her heart. Oh, all right, she's on a deadline to create a new toy... whatever the cost. ||
||||= **Author's Notes** ||
|||| This piece was co-authored with [[*user Crashington]] as part of [[[collaboration-contest|Collab-Con 2019]]]. ||
